Display Key Fields

Validate that the highlight panel displays the following fields on the Decision record page:

Decision Name

Status

Owner

Created Date

Last Modified Date

Role-Based Button Visibility

Show Edit, Delete, and Clone buttons only to users with Edit permission on the Decision record.

Show View Details button to all users with read access.

Validate that System Admins see all buttons.

Validate that Read-only users see no action buttons.

Dynamic Behavior

Ensure that field values refresh dynamically when record data is updated.

Ensure that button visibility updates automatically when a different user with different permissions logs in.
